    "This implies that both males and females are equally likely to share their experiences about a product or service, such as ChatGPT.",
    "On the other hand, the positive relationship between age and WOM can be understood from the perspective of life stage theory and accumulated experience.",
    "Older individuals, due to their broader life experiences and more diverse networks, may be more prone to sharing their experiences and opinions with others.",
